headline: Q3 wrap-up: Top stock performers & 2 reasons for a bullish Q4
summary: AppLovin (APP), Warner Bros. Discovery (WBD), Western Digital (WDC), and Intel (INTC) were some of the top-performing stocks in the third quarter of 2025. Looking ahead to the fourth quarter, Hennion & Walsh chief investment officer Kevin Mahn says two factors are driving his expectations for a fruitful final quarter.
